[{"id": 260710, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5200, "text": "TODO CUANTO hay en los cielos y todo cuanto hay en la tierra proclama la infinita gloria de Dios: Suya es la soberan\u00eda, y a \u00c9l es debida toda alabanza; y s\u00f3lo \u00c9l tiene poder para disponer cualquier cosa."}, {"id": 260711, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5201, "text": "\u00c9l es quien os ha creado: y entre vosotros hay quienes niegan esta verdad, y entre vosotros hay quienes creen [en ella]. Y Dios ve todo lo que hac\u00e9is."}, {"id": 260712, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5202, "text": "Ha creado los cielos y la tierra conforme a una verdad [intr\u00ednseca], y os ha formado \u2013y ha perfeccionado vuestra forma; y a \u00c9l es vuestro retorno."}, {"id": 260713, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5203, "text": "Conoce todo lo que hay en los cielos y en la tierra; y conoce todo lo que ocult\u00e1is y todo lo que hac\u00e9is p\u00fablico: pues Dios conoce perfectamente lo que hay en los corazones [de los hombres]."}, {"id": 260714, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5204, "text": "\u00bfNO HAN LLEGADO a conocimiento vuestro las historias de esos que, en el pasado, se negaron a reconocer la verdad? [La rechazaron --] y tuvieron que saborear el mal fruto de su conducta, y [en la Otra Vida] les aguarda un castigo [a\u00fan m\u00e1s] doloroso:"}, {"id": 260715, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5205, "text": "esto, porque una y otra vez vinieron a ellos sus enviados con las pruebas claras de la verdad, pero respondieron [siempre]: \u201c\u00bfEs que van a guiarnos simples mortales?\u201d Negaron pues la verdad y [le] dieron la espalda. Pero Dios no ten\u00eda necesidad [de ellos]: pues Dios es autosuficiente, digno de continua alabanza."}, {"id": 260716, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5206, "text": "\u00a1Los que se empe\u00f1an en negar la verdad aseguran que jam\u00e1s ser\u00e1n resucitados! Di: \u201c\u00a1Seguro que s\u00ed, por mi Sustentador! \u00a1Ciertamente, ser\u00e9is resucitados, y luego, ciertamente, se os har\u00e1 entender lo que hicisteis [en vida]! \u00a1Eso es f\u00e1cil para Dios!\u201d"}, {"id": 260717, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5207, "text": "\u00a1Creed, pues, [Oh hombres,] en Dios y en Su Enviado, y en la luz [de la revelaci\u00f3n] que hemos hecho descender [para vosotros]! Y Dios es plenamente consciente de lo que hac\u00e9is."}, {"id": 260718, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 556, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5208, "text": "[Pensad en ] el d\u00eda en que \u00c9l os reunir\u00e1 a todos para el D\u00eda de la [\u00daltima] Reuni\u00f3n --\u00a1ese D\u00eda de P\u00e9rdida y de Ganancia! Pues [en ese D\u00eda], a quien haya cre\u00eddo en Dios y haya obrado con rectitud, \u00c9l le borrar\u00e1 sus malas acciones, y le har\u00e1 entrar en jardines por los que corren arroyos, en los que morar\u00e1 m\u00e1s all\u00e1 del c\u00f3mputo del tiempo: \u00a1ese ser\u00e1 un magn\u00edfico triunfo!"}, {"id": 260719, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 490, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5209, "text": "Pero los que est\u00e1n empe\u00f1ados en negar la verdad y en desmentir Nuestros mensajes \u2013esos est\u00e1n destinados al fuego, en donde morar\u00e1n: \u00a1qu\u00e9 horrible destino!"}, {"id": 260720, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5210, "text": "NO HAY DESGRACIA que ocurra [al hombre] que no sea con la venia de Dios: as\u00ed pues, quien cree en Dios gu\u00eda su coraz\u00f3n [a esta verdad]; y Dios tiene conocimiento de todo."}, {"id": 260721, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5211, "text": "Obedeced, pues, a Dios, y obedeced al Enviado; y si dais la espalda, [sabed que] Nuestro Enviado est\u00e1 obligado s\u00f3lo a transmitir con claridad este mensaje:"}, {"id": 260722, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5212, "text": "\u00a1Dios \u2013no hay m\u00e1s deidad que \u00c9l! As\u00ed pues, que los creyentes pongan su confianza en Dios."}, {"id": 260723, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5213, "text": "\u00a1OH VOSOTROS que hab\u00e9is llegado a creer! \u00a1Ciertamente, algunos de vuestros c\u00f3nyuges y de vuestros hijos son enemigos vuestros: guardaos, pues, de ellos! Pero si pas\u00e1is por alto [sus faltas], sois tolerantes, y perdon\u00e1is \u2013entonces, ciertamente, Dios ser\u00e1 indulgente, dispensador de gracia."}, {"id": 260724, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5214, "text": "Vuestros bienes y vuestros hijos son s\u00f3lo una prueba y una tentaci\u00f3n, mientras que junto a Dios hay una magn\u00edfica recompensa."}, {"id": 260725, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5215, "text": "Sed, pues, todo lo conscientes de Dios que pod\u00e1is, escuchad[-le] y obedeced. Y gastad en limosnas por vuestro propio bien: pues, los que est\u00e1n a salvo de su propia codicia --\u00a1\u00e9sos, precisamente, alcanzar\u00e1n la felicidad!"}, {"id": 260726, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5216, "text": "Si hac\u00e9is a Dios un pr\u00e9stamo generoso, \u00c9l os lo devolver\u00e1 ampliamente incrementado, y perdonar\u00e1 vuestros pecados: pues Dios es sumamente agradecido, benigno;"}, {"id": 260727, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 64, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u063a\u0627\u0628\u0646", "surah_en_name": "At-Taghaabun", "surah_en_name_translation": "Mutual Disillusion", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 557, "ruku": 491, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5217, "text": "conoce cuanto est\u00e1 fuera del alcance de la percepci\u00f3n de los seres creados, y tambi\u00e9n cuanto pueden percibir --\u00a1el Todopoderoso, el Sabio!"}]